<header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="ph">The Second Review Conference of the Mine Ban Treaty: The Cartagena Summit on a Mine-Free World</h1>
</header>


<div class="grid">
    <div class="grid__cell unit-2-3">
        <div class="article-page">
            <p class="standfirst">29 November - 4 December 2009, Cartagena, Colombia </p>
            <p>Hundreds of representatives of States Parties to the Mine Ban Treaty, some states not party, international organizations, UN agencies, the International Committee of the Red Cross and the ICBL gathered in Cartagena, Colombia, from 29 November - 4 December 2009, for the Second Review Conference of the Mine Ban Treaty. This Review Conference aimed at assessing challenges in the universalization and full implementation of the Mine Ban Treaty, and taking stock of progress made since the First Review Conference in Nairobi, Kenya, in 2004.</p>

                    <div class="article-image">
                        <img src="/media/949595/Mission_Possible_logo_english.jpg" alt="" title="">
                    </div>

            <p class="standfirst"></p>

            <p>See also the <a href="http://www.cartagenasummit.org/" target="_blank">Second Review Conference webpage on the official convention website</a>.</p>
<p class="subheading"><a name="one" href="#one">Statements &amp; Updates</a></p>
<p class="subheading"><a href="#two">Press Releases &amp; Press Kit</a></p>
<p class="subheading"><a href="#three">Other Documents</a></p>
